    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The purpose of this memo is to define a general framework for particular metrics to be developed by the IETF's IP Performance Metrics effort.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
